{"tid":2071644,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚耀宗：今天不會公布草案條文","createTime":"2020-06-20T04:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T21:03:48.000Z","uid":5195,"like":18,"dislike":204,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"09be7366f9d92ad87dab22325fe33f7ca5bccd8e","tid":2071644,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:10:14.000Z","msg":"一連三日的人大常委會會議今早閉幕，今次會議議程之一是審議「港區國安法草案」。有份到北京出席會議的全國人大常委譚耀宗回應Topick查詢時表示，會議上只是初審「港區國安法」草案，指今天不會公布草案條文。<br />\n<br />\n今次常委會會議是首次審議港區國安法，按慣例，草案需經三審才表決，但若有意見較一致的法案，亦可在一次會議內審議及通過。至於人大常委會會否在本月底加開會議，或在8月份的下一次常委會會議中審議「港區國安法」，譚耀宗表明，未收到通知，亦未有回應草案條文是否有需要作修改。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9ab1105cd93453dcb1a503eb663c3cb3194b0d","tid":2071644,"uid":173849,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"五毛：抗爭失敗，唔好出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac9b3bc616e47bc784e501b39f246189f934f69","tid":2071644,"uid":24036,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"你都無權 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af17b92df494241b3b3a2ed5db3d302ac96ca152","tid":2071644,"uid":85252,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:14:33.000Z","msg":"即係意見唔一致?<br />\n係咪有人大想顛覆國家?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9e66d55e10d240fe5501e104c4846e6b423358","tid":2071644,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.r